I"<h3 id="timezone-of-date">Timezone of Date</h3>

<p>In order to accurately record the release date of a post, you should not only set up the <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">timezone</code> of <code class="language-plaintext filepath highlighter-rouge">_config.yml</code> but also provide the postâ€™s timezone in variable <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">date</code> of its Front Matter block. Format: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">+/-TTTT</code>, e.g. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">+0800</code>.</p>

